### Welcome to my GitHub.
I have been coding since January of 2016. Attended Gainesville Dev Academy where we learned the Mean stack. We've made several projects. In my GitHub some of my projects have been a calculater usung javascript , a weather app using an api, image search app using angular and an api and more. I really enjoy it, I've noticed my skills fall on the more visual side of things.
